<div class="heads green">
    <h2>What is the 1xBet Lucky Friday Bonus?</h2>
</div>

<div class="callout">

    <p>Lucky Friday is a permanent promotion for already registered players that allows you to obtain a 100 euro bonus to your account, depending on the deposit. </p>
    <p>To participate in it, the user must:</p>

    <ul>
        <li>Register on the company's website or log in through your account</li>
        <li>Go to the promo page and agree to participate in the Lucky Friday promotion on 1xBet</li>
        <li>Do a deposit on your account for at least 1 euro on Friday</li>
        <li>Be sure that the bonus account was replenished after the main one for an amount equal to 100% of the deposit (no more than 100 euros)</li>
        <li>According to the rules of 1xbet, the bonus is credited automatically if you have filled in all the fields in your personal data in your personal account. In addition, there should be a check mark in the "Take part in bonus promotions" field in your personal account.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>1XBet betting company knows that most of the sporting events start on Friday. For this reason, it has developed a special offer. It is aimed at actively betting on weekends. As part of the promotion, any player who made a deposit on Friday has the opportunity to receive up to 100 euros to his account.</p>

</div>


<div class="heads blue">
    <h3>How to win back the ‚ÄúLucky Friday‚Äù bonus in 1xBet?</h3>
</div>

<div class="callout">

<p class='center'>
        <amp-img alt="lucky friday" src="../../images/screenshoots/1xbet-lucky-friday2.png"   width="220" height="500"></amp-img><br>
    </p>

    <p>The main condition is that you should use it on Friday. This bonus does not apply to other days.  The second important rule is that the results of the events, respectively, and the bets placed, must also be announced on Friday. Otherwise, it will be canceled.</p>
    <p>To do this, you need to perform some simple conditions:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Make <b>Express bets</b> calculated in the <b>next 24 hours</b></li>
        <li>The <b>number of events</b> in the express is <b>at least 3</b>, the minimum coefficient for each of them - <b>1.40</b></li>
        <li>Betting events should be from various disciplines ‚Äî football, hockey, basketball, futsal, tennis and others</li>
        <li>The total amount of bets on all coupons must be <b>at least three times</b> more than the bonus amount. If the bonus is 100 euros, then the amount of bets is at least 300 euros</li>
        <li>The next bet can be concluded only after the previous one is calculated. For this reason, many people prefer to win back the Friday bonus in live mode</li>
    </ul>

    <blockquote><b>IMPORTANT</b>
        <p>When you win, the amount from the bonus account is transferred to the main account, but no more than the amount of the initially accrued bonus.</p>
    </blockquote>

</div>

