    <h3>For Example</h3>
</div>

<div class="callout">

    <p>You have topped up the Main Account for 50 euros. This means that the Bonus account was also automatically replenished by 50 euros.</p>
    <p>Place a bet from the bonus account. In total, you need to place bets for 150 euros (the amount is three times more than the bonus).
    </p>
    <p><i>Coupon 1</i></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Choose 3 or more sporting events with a coefficient of at least 1.40</li>
        <li>You bet "Express", for example, 45 euros</li>
        <li>Confirm the coupon and wait for the end of the games.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You have 105 euros left unspent. Make express bets using the same algorithm. In order to win back the bonus, the game must end before midnight. Otherwise, the bonus will burn.</p>

</div>

<div class="heads brown">
    <h3>Other terms of the promotion</h3>
</div>

<div class="callout">

    <p>The general terms of the 1xBet Happy Friday promotion are clear, but there are some nuances that you should be aware of. Firstly, this promotion cannot be combined with other promotions, that is, if you have active bonuses, then the Lucky Friday bonus will not be available. Secondly, participation in the promotion is available to users who regularly place bets. Thirdly, the bets for which the refund was made are not included in the offset. And most importantly: until all the conditions of the promotion are met, the player cannot withdraw funds from his account.</p>
    <p>Place your bets according to the rules and earn money with 1xBet!</p>

    
